CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 21, 2007

[Cite as 11121/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-6140.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2007-1654. State ex rel. Bozsik v. Court of Appeals, Ninth Appellate Dist.

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
